                "name": "Undersized Weapons",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "Although an oronci is Large, its upper torso is the same size as that of a Medium humanoid. As a result, oronci wield weapons as if they were one size category smaller than their actual size (Medium for most oronci)."
